            <div class="tre-profile-about-content">
            	<h2>About Agent</h2>
                <p>With a make-it-happen attitude and a solid reputation for professionalism and integrity, Nancy has been setting the standard as a Real Estate professional for over a decade. Her volume and production have consistently increased year to year and her accolades tell a similar story. With over $400 million in closed sales over her career, Nancy has been named a Chicago Association of Realtors Top Producer annually since 2005 and has earned her place as Senior Vice President at Jameson Sotheby's International Realty.</p>
<p>A "start to finish" broker, Nancy expertly and thoroughly guides her clients through the buying and selling of their home. She prides herself on her hands-on involvement at all stages of the process and will go to great lengths to help clients attain their real estate goals. Clients find comfort in her kind and straight-forward demeanor, effective communication and problem-solving abilities. Her winning combination of aggressiveness, tenacity and strategy results in loyal clients and her excellent reputation in the brokerage community.</p>
<p>Born and raised on the North Shore and living in Chicago for 18 years, Nancy possesses an extensive knowledge of Chicago real estate and is known for her expertise in matching the right properties with the right client. She enjoys touring the city with clients to share her local expertise and knowledge on the school systems and area highlights. Her love of real estate combined with her experience has earned her the respect and repeat business of her clients.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tre-profile-about-row tre-profile-about-more">
    	<div class="wrap">
        	<div class="tre-profile-about-more-content">
            <p>As founder and former Managing Broker of JDL Brokerage Company, Nancy has a comprehensive new construction background and is responsible for sell outs totaling over $300 million. Her knowledge of the home construction process has proven to be invaluable to her clients.</p>
<p>Nancy holds a degree in Business from the University of Wisconsin-Madison. Prior to her real estate career, Nancy had a successful career at Accenture, a renowned global consulting company in the fields of marketing and advertising.</p>
<p>Nancy lives in Chicago's West Lakeview neighborhood with her husband and three children.</p>
